In [72]:

#function to define margin of error
def m_e(z, st, n):
    res = (z * st) / n**(1/2)
    return res
In [259]:
def C_I(mean, mi):
    u1 = round(mean-mi, 2)
    v1 = round(mean+mi, 2)
    res = [u1, v1]
    return res
In [260]:
